\begin_inset Formula $a_{j}$
\end_inset

, with the probability 
\begin_inset Formula $|C_{J}|^{2}$
\end_inset

.
 This causes the state to collapse to 
\begin_inset Formula $\psi_{j}$
\end_inset

.
 now take a second measurement of the observable 
\begin_inset Formula $B$
\end_inset

