\begin_inset Formula 
\[
F_{z}=-\frac{\partial V}{\partial z}=-g_{l}\mu_{B}m_{l}\frac{\partial B_{z}}{\partial z}
\]

\end_inset

This then gives a means to measure 
\begin_inset Formula $m_{l}$
\end_inset

 and hence get 
\begin_inset Formula $L_{z}$
\end_inset

 of the electron.
